Class AliasesDeserializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonDeserializer<Map<String,List<JacksonMonolingualTextValue>>>
      • org.wikidata.wdtk.datamodel.json.jackson.AliasesDeserializer

  • public class AliasesDeserializer
extends com.fasterxml.jackson.databind.JsonDeserializer<Map<String,List<JacksonMonolingualTextValue>>>
    A deserializer implementation for the aliases in an JacksonTermedStatementDocument.

    It implements a workaround to cope with empty aliases being represented as "aliases":[] despite its declaration as map and not as list or array. This is neither nice nor fast, and should be obsolete as soon as possible.

    Author:
    Fredo Erxleben
    See Also:
    JacksonTermedStatementDocument.setAliases(Map)
